{"text_id":163632,"tokens":["The"," (","classical",")"," problem"," of"," characterizing"," and"," enumer","ating"," permutations"," that"," can"," be"," sorted"," using"," two"," stacks"," connected"," in"," series"," is"," still"," largely"," open","."," In"," the"," present"," paper"," we"," address"," a"," related"," but"," different"," problem",","," namely"," the"," complexity"," of"," sorting"," permutations"," by"," a"," sequence"," of"," stack"," operations"," using"," two"," stacks","."," Specifically",","," given"," a"," permutation"," pi",","," we"," seek"," a"," shortest"," sequence"," of"," stack"," operations"," (","push"," and","or"," pop",")"," that"," transforms"," pi"," into"," the"," identity"," permutation"," e","."," Our"," main"," result"," is"," a"," polynomial","-","time"," algorithm"," that"," solves"," this"," problem"," for"," permutations"," of"," length"," n"," with"," bounded"," number"," of"," inver","sions","."," Specifically",","," we"," show"," that"," if"," pi"," has"," at"," most"," k"," inver","sions",","," then"," it"," can"," be"," sorted"," using"," a"," sequence"," of"," O"," (","k","log"," n",")"," stack"," operations","."," Our"," approach"," is"," based"," on"," a"," new"," combinatorial"," character","ization"," of"," sequences"," of"," stack"," operations"," that"," sort"," a"," permutation","."," This"," character","ization"," allows"," us"," to"," express"," the"," problem"," of"," sorting"," permutations"," by"," stack"," operations"," as"," a"," variant"," of"," the"," well","-","known"," shortest"," common"," super","sequence"," problem",","," and"," to"," apply"," existing"," techniques"," from"," this"," area"," to"," obtain"," our"," result","."," Our"," algorithm"," compares"," favorably"," with"," previously"," known"," algorithms"," for"," the"," problem",","," which"," either"," had"," exponential"," running"," time"," in"," the"," worst"," case",","," or"," yielded"," results"," only"," for"," restricted"," classes"," of"," permutations","."," We"," also"," provide"," some"," experimental"," evidence"," that"," suggests"," that"," our"," algorithm"," performs"," well"," on"," random"," permutations"," with"," few"," inver","sions","."],"sub_source":"sci_gen","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}